<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.6">
<l>ceppiḷa meṉmulait tēvaki naṅkaikkuc</l>
<l>coppaṭat tōṉṟit toṟuppāṭi yōmvaitta</l>
<l>tuppamum pālun tayirum viḻuṅkiya</l>
<l>yappaṉvan tappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having been born well to the Lady Devakī</l>
<l rend="indent">with young, soft breasts [like] copper pots,</l>
<l>Appaṉ who was placed in our village of cattle herds,</l>
<l>who devoured the ghee, milk, and curds,</l>
<l>comes and is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
